#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.223"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.223:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.223:0.2"
msgid "23. Dīghacārikavagga"
msgstr "23. Long Wandering"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.223:0.3"
msgid "223. Atinivāsasutta"
msgstr "223. Overstaying"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.258"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.223:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, ādīnavā atinivāse."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five drawbacks of overstaying."

msgctxt "an5.223:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.223:1.3"
msgid ""
"Bahubhaṇḍo hoti bahubhaṇḍasannicayo, bahubhesajjo hoti "
"bahubhesajjasannicayo, bahukicco hoti bahukaraṇīyo byatto kiṅkaraṇīyesu, "
"saṃsaṭṭho viharati gahaṭṭhapabbajitehi ananulomikena gihisaṃsaggena, tamhā "
"ca āvāsā pakkamanto sāpekkho pakkamati."
msgstr ""
"You have a lot of stuff and store it up. You have a lot of medicine and "
"store it up. You have a lot of duties and responsibilities, and become an "
"expert in whatever needs to be done. You mix closely with laypeople and "
"renunciates, socializing inappropriately like a layperson. And when you "
"leave that monastery, you miss it."

msgctxt "an5.223:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ādīnavā atinivāse."
msgstr "These are the five drawbacks of overstaying."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.223:2.1"
msgid "Pañcime, bhikkhave, ānisaṃsā samavatthavāse."
msgstr ""
"There are these five benefits of staying for a reasonable length of time."

msgctxt "an5.223:2.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.223:2.3"
msgid ""
"Na bahubhaṇḍo hoti na bahubhaṇḍasannicayo, na bahubhesajjo hoti na "
"bahubhesajjasannicayo, na bahukicco hoti na bahukaraṇīyo na byatto "
"kiṅkaraṇīyesu, asaṃsaṭṭho viharati gahaṭṭhapabbajitehi ananulomikena "
"gihisaṃsaggena, tamhā ca āvāsā pakkamanto anapekkho pakkamati."
msgstr ""
"You don’t have a lot of stuff and store it up. You don’t have a lot of "
"medicine and store it up. You don’t have a lot of duties and "
"responsibilities, and become an expert in whatever needs to be done. You don’"
"t mix closely with laypeople and renunciates, socializing inappropriately "
"like a layperson. And when you leave that monastery, you don’t miss it."

msgctxt "an5.223:2.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ānisaṃsā samavatthavāse”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are the five benefits of staying for a reasonable length of time.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.223:2.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
